moduleTitle: Practicum in Online Learning in Music
prerequisite: Fourth year status in music or permission of instructor
moduleDescription: Students will learn the current methods and pedagogical approaches to teaching music over the Internet. Students will engage with musicians around the world in lessons, classes and workshops, both as instructors and participants.
faculty: YONG SIEW TOH CONSERVATORY OF MUSIC
